oduplication Service.", "Available on microfilm from ProQuest, <2001->", "Some issues bear edition statement: City edition; some issues bear statement: National edition. It is unclear whether National edition is truly a separately published geographic edition, or whether both editions may have been issued as part of the same title, especially since other edition statements such as \"Church edition\" appear on occasional issues, <1932->, and the issue for July 3, 1932, bears the statement, \"2 sections, get both!\", which may indicate that the national and city \"editions\" actually indicate two sections of one issue.", "Latest issue consulted: Vol. 85, issue 22 (Jan. 3/9, 2013) (microfilm surrogate)."], "other_formats": ["https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp//gu/batch_gu_goblin_ver01/data/sn82015425/00529040982/1958040901/1958040901_1.xml", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn82015425/marcxml"], "other_title": ["Published occasionally in 1934-1945 as: Atlanta world"], "place_of_publication": "Atlanta, Georgia", "raw_lccn": "sn 82015425 ", "reel_numbers": ["00529040982"], "source_group": "ndnp/gu", "subjects": ["African Americans--Georgia--Atlanta--Newspapers", "African American newspapers--Georgia", "Atlanta (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Fulton County (Ga.)--Newspapers", "African American newspapers", "African Americans", "Georgia", "Georgia--Atlanta", "Georgia--Fulton County", "United States--Georgia--Fulton--Atlanta"], "title": "Atlanta daily world (Atlanta, Georgia), April 9, 1958, (City Edition)"}, "language": ["english"], "languages": [{"english": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=language:english&fo=json"}], "library_of_congress_control_number": "sn82015425", "location": ["fulton county", "atlanta", "georgia", "united states", "fulton"], "location_city": ["atlanta"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["fulton"], "location_state": ["georgia"], "locations": [{"atlanta": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=location:atlanta&fo=json"}, {"fulton": "https:/